    "millsfield:images_texts": [
      "malaysian airline system\nmas747\nCOMING APRIL 1982",
      "AIR MAIL\nThe MAS 747 has been planned for passenger comfort and\nconvenience. Carrying 18 cabin crew, with 11 gallies and 14\ntoilets, each zone will have its own designated facilities.\nAllowing for speedier service; better and quicker attention\nfrom cabin crew\nPowered by the latest Rolls Royce engines, there will be 8mm\nmovies and 14 channels of music _\n4 more than standard\nB747s.\nThe First Class has luxurious sleepers seats; 14 on the upper\ndeck and 16 on the lower deck. An elegant straight staircase\nconnects the 2 decks.\nBusiness Class, is in zone by itself with wide comfortable seats\nand only 8 abreast seating.\nThe three economy zones have colourful interiors to give the\nholiday makers a cheerful start to their vacation.\nComfort and convenience as only MAS can give — We treat you\nlike Gold.\n7 mas\nmalaysian airline system\nMAS B747\n2015166.2540"
    ],
